data.description: Price Adjustment on this beautiful home   Rare opportunity in Loudoun Valley Estates 2! Don't miss your chance to own this beautiful end unit town home. 4 bedrooms, 3.5 baths. Large open concept design with high ceilings, recessed lights and crown molding. The gourmet kitchen, is beautiful with dark cherry cabinets, granite counters, stainless steel appliances complete with a gas range. The primary suite includes a large walk in closest and an attached bath with standing shower and dual sinks. The additional bedrooms are are great size. The lower level bedroom is perfect for an office, mother in law suite or a study convenient with a full bath on the same level. Close to Silver Line Metro, entertainment, restraints and major road ways.
